### ============================================================
### query-burst-msa ranking-service API
### Base URL: http://localhost:18112
### ============================================================

# @no-log

### Health
GET http://localhost:18112/actuator/health

### ============================================================
### [DATA INIT]
### ============================================================

### 테스트 데이터 적재 시작
POST http://localhost:18112/api/data-init

### 테스트 데이터 적재 상태 확인
GET http://localhost:18112/api/data-init/status

### ============================================================
### [RANKING]
### ============================================================

### 실시간 랭킹 - 최근 1시간
GET http://localhost:18112/api/rankings/realtime

### 실시간 랭킹 - 최근 6시간 TOP 20
GET http://localhost:18112/api/rankings/realtime?windowHours=6&size=20

### 실시간 랭킹 - 최근 24시간 TOP 50
GET http://localhost:18112/api/rankings/realtime?windowHours=24&size=50
